    <p id="header">Chapter 1
      <br>Morning Ritual</p>
    <p id="text">Usually when I wake up in the morning for a skateboarding packed day, I always start off with a cigarette to calm my mind and try visualise what types of spots and tricks I would like to visit and skate. </p>
  </div>

  <div id="container2">
    <img id="image" src="http://40.media.tumblr.com/3fc3f88add27e7fa2f4c5dc607b15030/tumblr_n63uviyayQ1qi26jgo1_500.jpg" style="width: 1000px" />
    <p id="header2">Chapter 2 <br>Skate Gear</p>
    <p id="text2">After the morning ritual, I like to prepare the most important tool for a skateboarder besides his or her board, the shoes. I prefer the Nike SB Stefan Janoski because of its pointed toe and heel pouch which performs well with my skate style.
    </p>
  </div>

